name: Snapshot During Holiday
description:
This photo I took during a holiday in Bali when I was high school in 2014. I deliberately changed it to black and white to increase the nostalgia that was in it.

At the time, I didn't have a basic understanding of photography. With my mother's pocket camera, I enjoy doing snapshots of objects and sights that I find interesting.

I learned a lot about the changes that have been made in me. I learned a lot about photography since 2016 and got myself to this point and will continue to learn over and over again.

Thank you so much for all the support so far. I am so grateful to be in such a supportive community.
